'''Rosario Alfred Fernandes''' (5 August 1932 − 21 October 2003), zaka '''Alfred Rose''' mhonn volkhotat zaun aslo ek [[tiatr]]ist, zaka sogleavon famad [[Konknni]] kantar korpi mhunnunk xektat. Tennem romans-ui boroileo. Alfred Rosan [[Amchem Noxib]] ani Sukhachem Sopon, hi cholchitranim kam kelem.

Famad zallo Konkani Tiatr Palkacher, Alfred Rose hea navam. Tajem nav zaun aslem Rosario Alfred Fernandes. Zolmololo Augustache 5ver, 1932 hea vorsak, Calvim, Aldona hea Goemchea gavant. Tiatrist familint zolmolo ho Goemcho putt. Bapaichem nav A M B Rose ( Ambrose Fernandes) ani Avoichem nav Dolarosa Fernandes. Tiatrist C Alvares, anne taka mogan nav dil’lem Junior Rose. Alfred Rose anne aplo poilo part tiatrant 1943 vorsak kello. Alfred Rose hem nav tannem 1950 vorsak ghetlem. 

==== Fattbhuim ====

Tacho zolm  5 Agostt 1932 hea disa zalo.  Tachem Maichem nanv Doloroza ani Bapaichem nanv Ambroz aslolem.  1949 hea vorsak Sant Xavier iscollantlean S.S.C.  pas zalo. Tachea uprant tannem bankechi porikxa dili. Tea porikxent pas zalea uprant  National Overseas  ani Grindlay’s hea bankamni tannem nokri keli. Larson ani  Toubro ani toxench Gulfant anik eke bankant tannem aplo vaur kelo. ‘Alfritz Goa General stores  hea namvan tannem svotacho posro ukto kelo ani apli bholaiken zata title meren tannem to choloilo. 

