==== Alfred Rozache kaim vikrom ====


Modor  Teresa  jivi astana tichea jivitacher adarun  aslolem  tannem 1951 hea vorsa poilem git gailem. Toxench A. R. Souza,  Kid Boksor ani Rejinald Fernandis hea monxanchea jivitacher ani toxench tanchea vauracher kantar tannem gaileant. Ghumvte machyer 1958 vorsa tannem poilo tiatr sador kelo. ‘Director Saib’ (1961) ho tiatr thambnasotona (Non stop) dakhoupi to poilo tiatrist. Tiatrachea itihasant aplem lognachem amontronn konknnitlean chappi to poilo tiatrist. ‘Boglantt’ hea filmant tannem ekach disa bhitor atth gitam rekord kelim.  Ekach disa bhitor itlim kataram rekord korpi to poilo tiatrist ani konknni filmachea itihasant hem poilem paut ghoddlem.

==== Alfredd rozan kel'lem borop ====

Tannem don kadombreo ani 10 kantarache jhele solfa soit ujvaddak haddleat. Tea bhair  ‘Zomnintli bhirant’ hem ek vinodi pustok chaplam.  Toxench tannem potrokaritechea mollar dolle dipkaupi vaur kel'lo amkam pollounk melltta. Goa Times, Sot uloi, Cine times hea  nemalleancher tannem aplem borop kelam.


====Tiatrachea mollar taka mellole kaim mukutt ====

‘The Melody King’,  ‘The living musical Legend’,  ‘Father of Konknni cassettes’,  ‘The Singing Sensation, ‘ Music Maestro’,  ‘ The singer with a panama hat’,  ‘Magic Wand’,  ‘ Konknni Ambassador’, ‘International Super Star’,  ‘Gigantic Figure of Konknni Stage’,  ‘ The Sultan of Swing’, ‘Sangit Sagor’, ‘ The Man with the golden voice’,  ‘Alfies voice is a gift’,  ‘Sab kuch Alfie’,. 

Marann tachea so daskachea tiatristponnant, Alfik fivnneo ghalun talleancho ximvor korun yeukar dilo. Nimanne 2-3 vorsam, Okttoborache 23 tarker Alfred Rose hachea nikipinnea (zomnint purop) vellar, tiatristamni ani tachea tiatr mogeamni Alfak talleo pettoun nimanno adeus kelo.


